page.title: 16T.V. PROGRAMES I LIKE
page.content: I have a lot of favourite programmes but these are my very favourite ones starting with cartoons.Dungeons and Dragons this cartoon is about a little man called Dongeon Master who leads 7 children into lots of adventures against Vengar and his flying horse who wants there magic weapons and in 1 episode they meet at the dragons grave yard where their weapons are most powerful and they beat Vengar.My favourite childrens films are Street Hawk and Knight Rider. Street Hawk is about a moter cycle that goes over 100 M.P.H.He is a policeman as well and he has a friend who he keeps in contact with and his friend built Street Hawk.Knight Rider is similar only it is about a black car that has turbo boost,ejector seat,parachute and lots more buttons.In the series he helps people and solves crimes.
